trans-unit.source: Draws an elliptical arc from the current point to (x, y) using absolute coordinates. The center (cx, cy) of the ellipse is calculated automatically to satisfy the constraints imposed by the other parameters. largeArcFlag and sweepFlag contribute to the automatic calculations and help determine how the arc is drawn. If largeArcFlag is TRUE then draw the larger of the available arcs. If sweepFlag is true, then draw the arc matching a clock-wise rotation.

El centro (cx, cy) de la elipse se calcula automáticamente para satisfacer las restricciones impuestas por los otros parámetros. largeArcFlag y sweepFlag contribuyen a los cálculos automáticos y ayudan a determinar cómo se dibuja el arco.
